      "id": "30bb68e8cb0dfbe4",
      "text": " Bonuses act as incentives to attract new users or to retain existing ones. Malus is the opposite of bonus – typically a charge on the conversion back into legal tender – and is a straightforward way of financing the bonus system."
    },
